&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;You&#39;re not afraid to navigate up and down a deep technical stack. You don&#39;t define yourself by the tools you know, only by the problems you solve.&lt;/li&gt;
