&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data-Driven Insights:&lt;/strong&gt; Deliver analysis that helps inform team performance in market, product utilization, forecasting insights, and revenue trends for BD.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
