&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Product Manager to own a security-critical blockchain product that sits at the intersection of smart contract infrastructure and end-user signing workflows. The product has smart contracts, an API surface, and a frontend interface - you need to care deeply about all parts. We have a high security bar and need someone who understands exactly why that bar exists and how to build product that meets it without compromising usability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end product development - vision, roadmap, requirements, and execution from 0→1 and beyond.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with engineers to define product requirements, API surfaces, and frontend interaction patterns across multi-party signing workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
