&lt;li&gt;Engage constantly with the multisig and smart contract wallet ecosystem; understand how teams use these tools today and where the gaps are.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex blockchain interactions into product experiences that are clear, safe, and usable without stripping away capability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive alignment across engineering, design, and BD - overcommunicate vision and decisions tailored to technical and non-technical stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unblock engineering, drive momentum, and take ownership for outcomes end-to-end.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT YOU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
