&lt;li&gt;Build, monitor, and maintain blockchain node infrastructure for a variety of DLTs, ensuring reliability and performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product and platform engineers to proactively address reliability, scalability, and observability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop scalable infrastructure using code, with a focus on Kubernetes Helm charts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automate incident detection, triage, and resolution processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in the on-call rotation for systems owned by the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
